{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":70,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"李坏","listener":"char_gong_sun_xian_sheng","text":"我明白你的意思。你出手，并不是为了求胜，只不过为了要找一个值得你出手的对象而已。成败胜负根本就没有放在你的心上。","tone":"认真","chapter":10,"line_start":12,"line_end":14},{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"李坏","listener":"char_gong_sun_xian_sheng","text":"如果不配让你出手的人，就算跪在地上求你，你也不会对他伸出一根手指。","tone":"认真","chapter":10,"line_start":16,"line_end":18},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_xian_sheng","speaker_name":"公孙先生","listener":"char_li_huai","text":"我就知道你会明白的，如果你不明白，世上还有谁能明白？","tone":"感慨","chapter":10,"line_start":22,"line_end":23},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_xian_sheng","speaker_name":"公孙先生","listener":"char_li_huai","text":"如果我不败，这世上还有谁败？","tone":"豪迈","chapter":10,"line_start":24,"line_end":25},{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"李坏","listener":"char_gong_sun_xian_sheng","text":"我从本不拍别人的马屁，可是今天我们就算是生死之敌，就算我在顷刻之间就会死在你手里，或者我在顷刻之间就会杀了你。我也要先说一句话。","tone":"严肃","chapter":10,"line_start":32,"line_end":34},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_xian_sheng","speaker_name":"公孙先生","listener":"char_li_huai","text":"你说。","tone":"平静","chapter":10,"line_start":36,"line_end":36},{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"李坏","listener":"char_gong_sun_xian_sheng","text":"公孙先生，你虽然永败无胜，可是你虽败犹荣，我佩服你。","tone":"认真","chapter":10,"line_start":38,"line_end":38},{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"李坏","listener":null,"text":"我非常感谢，你愿意把我当做你第五个对手，我实在觉得非常荣幸。","tone":"认真","chapter":10,"line_start":52,"line_end":53},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_xian_sheng","speaker_name":"公孙先生","listener":"char_li_huai","text":"那也是没法子的事。我已经收了别人三万两黄金来换你一条命。","tone":"淡然","chapter":10,"line_start":56,"line_end":57},{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"李坏","listener":"char_gong_sun_xian_sheng","text":"我真想不到，我的命居然有这么值钱。","tone":"调侃","chapter":10,"line_start":62,"line_end":62},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_xian_sheng","speaker_name":"公孙先生","listener":"char_li_huai","text":"我们夫妻一直都很守信约的，只要约一订，无论在什么情况下，我们都会守约的。","tone":"严肃","chapter":10,"line_start":64,"line_end":65},{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"李坏","listener":"char_gong_sun_xian_sheng","text":"我也是个很有原则的人，而且我现在还不想死，所以我虽然很佩服你，我还是决心要让你再败一次。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":70,"line_end":70}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_li_huai","name":"李坏","alias":["小李飞刀传人"],"identity":"江湖游侠","faction":null,"role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":null,"one_line":"小李飞刀的后人，武功深不可测，行事洒脱不羁","personality":{"traits":["洒脱","重义气","幽默","自信","有原则","尊敬对手"],"speech_style":"随性洒脱，说话直率","temperament":"外冷内热"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_gong_sun_xian_sheng","type":"对手","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"互相尊敬的生死对手"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[10],"source_refs":[{"chapter":10,"line_start":10,"line_end":10,"text":"这道理，李坏懂。"},{"chapter":10,"line_start":12,"line_end":14,"text":"他对公孙先生说，你出手，并不是为了求胜"}]},{"id":"char_gong_sun_xian_sheng","name":"公孙先生","alias":[],"identity":"江湖隐士","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":null,"one_line":"每战必败的神秘高手，心高气傲，虽败犹荣","personality":{"traits":["心高气傲","重信守诺","内敛深沉","孤独","尊敬对手"],"speech_style":"冷淡从容，暗含深意","temperament":"孤傲自持"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_li_huai","type":"对手","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"互相尊敬的生死对手"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[10],"source_refs":[{"chapter":10,"line_start":12,"line_end":14,"text":"他对公孙先生说，你出手，并不是为了求胜"},{"chapter":10,"line_start":56,"line_end":57,"text":"我已经收了别人三万两黄金来换你一条命"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
